902
01:05:19,000 --> 01:05:20,000
[SPEAKER_02] Introspekt, da.

903
01:05:20,000 --> 01:05:23,000
[SPEAKER_02] Vlatka Kalinić, buďte svašta lepoga počitati.

904
01:05:23,000 --> 01:05:24,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ćao, spok.

